        =========
        
        1.7.8 (2012-11-01)
        ------------------
        
        - Removed doctests.py that made tests of other packages fail.
          [thomasdesvenain]
        
        - Fix opening psd files with RGBA layers when A mode is not of type 65535 but 3.
          Fixes issue https://github.com/python-imaging/Pillow/issues/3
          [thomasdesvenain]
        
        
