        - UNDEF more types before including windows headers
          [mattip]
        
        1.7.6 (2012-01-20)
        ------------------
        
        - Bug fix: freetype not found on Mac OS X with case-sensitive filesystem
          [gjo]
        
        - Bug fix: Backport fix to split() after open() (regression introduced in PIL 1.1.7).
          [sfllaw]
        
